move

public void move(double dx,
                 double dy)
Move this AperiodicPart by (dx,dy). If dx is positive, a Segment (0,0,0) is added at the beginning of the AperiodicPart. If dx is negative, the resulting AperiodicPart defined over x < 0 is lost.

Parameters:
dx - the x-value by which this AperiodicPart is moved.
dy - the y-value by which this AperiodicPart is moved.

round

public void round()
Round all points that define this AperiodicPart. This includes all start points of all segments, all slopes, as well as px0, py0, pdy. All related values such as pyMin and pyMax are newly calculated.
